From cou.: 9 The coarse-grained model of dihydroxy taurine- or glycine-substituted bile salts used here is shown in Fig. 1. In the same figure we show the correspondence between the coarse-grained model and the molecular structure of taurochenodeoxycholate; we emphasize, however, that the model is also representative of other conjugated dihydroxy bile salts.
From Soup: 9 The coarse-grained model of dihydroxy taurine- or glycine-substituted bile salts used here is shown in Fig. 1 . In the same figure we show the correspondence between the coarse-grained model and the molecular structure of taurochenodeoxycholate; we emphasize, however, that the model is also representative of other conjugated dihydroxy bile salts.
